Now,
 $0.999$ is closer to $1$, and since $1$ is an integer, we have
\begin{align*}
\lfloor0.999\rfloor&=\boxed{0}.
\end{align*}
Next, $2.001$ is farther from $2$, so $2$ is the answer,
\begin{align*}
\lceil2.001\rceil&=\boxed{2}.
\end{align*}
Adding the two conclusions, $0+2=2$, and the final answer is
2. </answer>

